snippet.title: RocketStarz Ad 1
snippet.description:
Game: RocketStarz

Publisher: HHS Gaming

To obtain the game one must donate $5 to the gofundme listed below, money goes to St.Jude, and in return the participant will get a link to the game.

gofundme:
https://www.gofundme.com/f/high-school-game-devs-for-st-jude?qid=816bebdb5fa011f8e3b018ecabec2e55

More information about St. Jude Children's Research Hospital: St. Jude Children's Research Hospital is leading the way the world understands, treats and defeats childhood cancer and other life-threatening diseases. Our mission is clear: Finding cures. Saving children. Families never receive a bill from St. Jude for treatment, travel, housing or food - because all family should worry about is helping their child live. Please help St. Jude continue its mission by donating today.
